ng is... if you are not going to the server why give a damn what happens to it? huh?.. it's just like what some people say about pop music, who gives a crap if they listen to it? no prob. i'm not the one being brainwashed by crappy music. sorry if this is turning into an rant but please quit judging the legends server when it hasn't even been live for a week... people are still signing up. <br><br>lets just wait and see... <p><center><br><img src="http://a0.cpimg.com/image/8A/CA/8481930-eaf4-014B01B8-.jpg"><br><font color=purple><br><b><br></b></font><a href="http://www.mines.edu/students/a/averheyd/">\m/SPREAD THE SICKNESS\m/</a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usoneldarblackrose.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Soneldar Blackrose</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 101<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(2/2/02 5:39:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1265.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Alright... *Parental Advisory!*</span><hr size=1> If you ask me, the Legends server is attempting to do 3 things:<br><br>1.) Show off new things Verant has been putzing around with (BTW, to the people of Verant, YOU SHOULD BE WORKING ON THE LUCLIN BUGS, NOT THIS NEW SERVER YOU DUMBASSES!)<br><br>2.) Show that they are in the hole with some serious MMORPGs coming out and they want to contain their customers, avoiding profit losses.<br><br>and 3.) Attempt to succeed where FV failed.<br><br>I just payed a visit to DRo.com, and they were all in unison: Legends is going to fall flat on its face.  The transfer of characters leave the door wide open for ubers to come in and crash the party.  Also, the pushing forward of the story on just 1 server admits one thing: They want your money just for you